10 REM Minimal serial receiver - shows hex bytes
20 VDU 4
30 SYS "OS_SerialOp",0,6,0:REM 9600 8N1
40 SYS "OS_SerialOp",1,0:REM No parity
50 SYS "OS_SerialOp",5,7:REM Stream 7 input
60 mask%=&04
70 REPEAT
80   SYS "OS_SerialOp",4 TO s%
90   IF (s% AND mask%) THEN SYS "OS_SerialOp",2 TO b%:PRINT "~";~b%;" ";
100 UNTIL FALSE